These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, hip-hop, pop, indie
1. the fan of metal is on the left of the fan of indie##1
2. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the fan of pop##1
3. the fan of metal is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Music-Genre   | pop | hip-hop | metal | indie |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-2::.
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, cat, goat, horse
1. the owner of the horse is on the far right##1
2. the owner of the rabbit is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the goat is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |   2   |     3      |   4    |
| Pet   | rabbit | goat | cat | horse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, collecting, dancing, hiking
1. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
2. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2    |      3      |       4       |
| Hobby   | dancing | gardening | collecting | hiking |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-4::.
