1. the person driving the boat is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the snowmobile is on the far right##1
3. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |  2   |    3    |  4  |
| Transport   | boat | subway | skateboard | snowmobile |

